  <entry>
    <title>利用SSH push 代码到仓库</title>
    <link href="/2020/12/11/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8SSH%20push%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93/"/>
    <url>/2020/12/11/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8SSH%20push%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="首先配置SSH-KEY"><a href="#首先配置SSH-KEY" class="headerlink" title="首先配置SSH　KEY"></a>首先配置SSH　KEY</h3><p>具体可以参考这篇博客：<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/c9aa544a11d3">https://www.jianshu.com/p/c9aa544a11d3</a></p><h3 id="然后在terminal中"><a href="#然后在terminal中" class="headerlink" title="然后在terminal中"></a>然后在terminal中</h3><pre class=" language-hljs awk"><span class="hljs-regexp"><code class="language-hljs awk"><span class="hljs-regexp">//gi</span>t remote add XXX SSH ....git remote add ykq git@github.com:twtstudio/WePeiYang-Android.git<span class="hljs-regexp">//gi</span>t branch<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>查看分支* announcement</code></pre><p>然后可以用</p><pre class=" language-hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute"><code class="language-hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">git status -s</span></code></pre><p>查看是否已经add</p><p>然后</p><pre class=" language-hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">git</span> commit -m <span class="hljs-string"><code class="language-hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">git</span> commit -m <span class="hljs-string">"做了个人页面"</span></code></pre><pre class=" language-hljs armasm"><span class="hljs-symbol">git</span> <span class="hljs-keyword"><code class="language-hljs armasm"><span class="hljs-symbol">git</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">push</span> ykq announcement</code></pre><p>完成</p>]]></content>
    
    
